org.antfarmer.ejce.password

Class EncodedPasswordType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antfarmer.ejce.password.EncodedPasswordType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParameterizedType, UserType

    public class EncodedPasswordType
extends Object
implements UserType, ParameterizedType
    Hibernate UserType class which encodes password values transparently using a one-way hashing algorithm. This ensures data is stored in it's hashed form in persistent storage. Values returned in the application will be that of the hashed/encoded form.
